#Autonomous luggage carrier is a robot. The foremost idea of this bot is to carry  bulky luggage at customary stopping points, reducing human efforts and increasing the accuracy in the work and to serve the people.
A user can contact the robot using the Blynk app. As it receives the information, it traces the location of the customer and reaches him/her using GPS and Ultrasonic sensors and carries the luggage and follows the customer till he reaches the destination.  
